>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">OilAlpha <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i><br />TAG-41 <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i><br />TAG-62 <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?c=Yemen\" title=\"Search for all threat groups from Yemen\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/flags/Yemen.png\" alt=\"Yemen\" width=\"33\" height=\"20\" /> Yemen</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Information%20theft%20and%20espionage\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Information theft and espionage\" class=\"inlink\">Information theft and espionage</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2022</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "Since May 2022, Insikt Group has tracked an ongoing campaign by a threat group which is highly likely to have targeted entities associated with the non-governmental, media, international humanitarian, and development sectors. It is almost certain that the entities targeted shared an interest in Yemen, security, humanitarian aid, and reconstruction matters. It is highly likely that OilAlpha threat actors were involved in espionage activity, as handheld devices were targeted with remote access tools",
    "like SpyNote and SpyMax. Our assessment of the victimology suggests that the majority of the targeted entities were Arabic-language speakers and operated Android devices.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=njRAT\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use njRAT\" class=\"inlink\">njRAT</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=SpyMax\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use SpyMax\" class=\"inlink\">SpyMax</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=SpyNote%20RAT\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use SpyNote RAT\" class=\"inlink\">SpyNote RAT</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://go.recordedfuture.com/hubfs/reports/cta-2023-0516.pdf\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://go.recordedfuture.com/hubfs/reports/cta-2023-0516.pdf</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 21 June 2023</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=OilAlpha&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=OilAlpha&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Face